Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  由绮也终于要成为偶像啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  所以…已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…冬弥…我…绪方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮  我听不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.11,0:00:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这里那么吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单曲「Trisatto」创造了50万张热卖记录
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首张专辑「Darklist」也突破30万张
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六张单曲「Mac·the·Mac」首次突破100万张
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在登上人气顶峰之后的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自行创立绪方制作公司  并让自己的妹妹理奈出道后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为经营者  又兼任着作曲  制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是走上新的道路的绪方英二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而由绮是继理奈后  绪方制作公司培养的第二位艺人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由…绮…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为前辈的绪方理奈  经常和她说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  在一起的时候总是聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是会紧张的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是前辈  其实更像是老师一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会训斥你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…是指绪方先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英二先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是理奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈的话倒不是像老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要说的话更像是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人经常在一起说笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  差不多到时间了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么最后能说一下今后的目标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  已经中午了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种工作都想尝试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演戏也想试试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是想像绪方理奈前辈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力唱歌  希望能快点出唱片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天做客Fresh  eye的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现役女子大学生的森川由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是股票及外汇市场早报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截至今天上午收盘  平均股价比上周下跌了32.40日元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收于16804.15日元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国际外汇市场的日元汇率为1美元兑换163.65日元…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:05:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥君也来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮  刚才电视里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是录像  你看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个傻瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在主持人面前乱说对理奈的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  由绮  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为好像也是想让我那样回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就故意装傻了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  我很坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮  要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  之后还有录像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是筱冢小姐  是我的经纪人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥君  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  总算是见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都带着很重的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布朗宁诗集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.21,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Robert  Browning：英国维多利亚时期的抒情诗人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伯特·布朗宁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过定不下报告的主题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说想看看  令人心跳的恋爱诗歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗总是让人沉醉于其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又充满忧郁…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道「哈梅伦的吹笛者」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:51.83,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈梅伦的吹笛者：布朗宁的作品之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹笛男爵的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之借你了  拿回去太麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布朗宁是那个切斯特顿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.69,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G·K·切斯特顿：英国短篇推理小说家 曾为布朗宁写过文艺评论
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  那个「热情的读者」 你也看那个评传了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的布朗神父探案集  有机会能借我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:14.00,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Father Brown 布朗神父是切斯特顿笔下的教士侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…现在就借也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七濑君说  她只要稍微有点时间就会来上课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天见到由绮了吗  美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  她不是没事老是美咲  美咲的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是这样  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后会越来越忙  见面机会会更少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  不好好抓紧她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听吗  藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长说可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说店长…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从叔叔升级而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拒绝掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去做吗…兼职的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真打算去做家庭教师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都来了为什么不做  也已经登记过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去图书馆  你们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  去还是不去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要打工不是吗  去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人也没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,echoes的地址我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔…不  店长也不是不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她一起去图书馆多好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经五年了啊  五年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也该下决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会以我的步调…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是借你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写个读后感给美咲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便我的那份报告也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲可是借给你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏美咲  我才从差点输给学分的危机中解脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了…今天的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天会借到这个  其实我是早就知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样无意识中绕了个弯子  做了那个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了睡过头  打工被解雇  然后不得不来大学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是遇到了由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦和现实是连接着的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:11:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲其实是为了让我和由绮见面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的推理如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花生君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰逊…啊  是哈德逊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种自认为越来越接近的想法真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  吹笛男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  今天的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥  要被听到了哦  被另一个女神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥  去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去  之后还要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,echoes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打网球的话我陪你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么叫哪壶不开提哪壶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥  等等  遥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  彰那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到由绮了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多亏了我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我不知道她还这么在意她哥哥那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后 她就再也没有拿起过球拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是那么被大家看好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国大赛的名次也不差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没办法啊  毕竟失去了最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法吗  这么放着她不管好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得  那家伙好像在慢慢崩溃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一直都是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小时候开始就是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是还没从打击中恢复而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也用不着这么生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改正
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我和由绮见面的女神似乎是遥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真羡慕你啊  周围全是女神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮可不是女神哦  跟你说了很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也听了很多次了  由绮是邻家女孩对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可到今天你是几个月没见到那邻家女孩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她刚刚搬到事务所准备的宿舍里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还没装好电话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地址呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被事务所那边封口了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮真的成为偶像了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  …
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子竟然那么老实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先  先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她们欺负了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们要你去买饮料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.61,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮小姐  能帮买点饮料来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁机…但是为什么  为什么由绮要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:06.72,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要  我也要  我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那场面很难拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不去买
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  当时我不在场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过目标是由绮的话  你在也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  是上周那件事的报复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了吧  直接找我说不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她们是不会去找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有备用的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…不合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  该去下一个工作的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？要我帮你跟制作人说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧  理奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我应该能解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  回来的时候我会再来看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别输啊  由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:12.99,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,echoes咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  《密室推理》这月的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是跟去图书馆比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说美咲的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《密室推理》的事啦  买不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:16:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都是在图书馆看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我所以去不成了  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚才想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰奇  谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写了首不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那位是由绮那的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方英二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由  由绮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在啦  怎么可能在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么绪方英二会来这？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是…什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长说  可以下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发今天的薪水了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么行  我们从上班到现在一个客人都没…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  不  能  收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你老爸看看如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就住附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我向那冷血动物低头？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近大学的课程比较紧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工不太顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想跟你谈谈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方理奈真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她一比  由绮真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  有请神田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:28.01,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红灯笼（居酒屋的俗称）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都不正确
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让我们看看正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确答案…正确答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  就那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍眼  你真碍眼  快滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:43.06,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确答案是在家里建了温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到由绮了啦  碍眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜头  笨蛋  你拍哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  谁啊  这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  藤井家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？由绮？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你不是在电视上…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是上周的录像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  吓到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收录刚刚才完  因为早上没能说上几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我当然在看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录像也录好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可爱啊  非常可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比平常更…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平常一样可爱  特别是见识了绪方理奈的可怕之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？她骂樱团那些女孩的录像放映了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为被剪掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  在那之后发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我也挺努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周会更有趣的  冬弥君一定要看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一定看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我从今天开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  在echoes吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真怀念啊  那里的手制芝士蛋糕很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个好像已经不卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彰君的叔叔还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  店长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮  我今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我会再给你打电话的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.05,0:24:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二页
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.74,0:24:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就被安排好的相遇  你相信吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.14,0:24:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album
